title: KJV Audio Bible - Narrated by Dan Wagner
description:
Audio version of the Holy Scripture in English.

I do recommend this audio recording. It is spoken in a slow pace without any background music, just voice. The narrator is a retired minister from California named Dan Wagner. It was recorded in 1999.

The chapters of the Old Testament have a distribution notice at the end. The chapters of the New Testament have no such notice. The notice explains that it's OK to distribute this recording for free.

Here are some technical details about the recording quality:

Audio
Format                      : MPEG Audio
Format version              : Version 2
Format profile              : Layer 3
Bit rate mode               : Constant
Bit rate                    : 32.0 Kbps
Channel(s)                  : 1 channel
Sampling rate               : 22.05 KHz
Compression mode            : Lossy
